Gavony	KEY:Provincial Origin ~ Gavony	TYPE:Innistrad Human ~ Provincial Origin.SpecialQuality	CATEGORY:Special Ability		DESC:Whether safe behind the walls of the High City of Thraben or out in the moors with little more than shuttered windows, barred doors, and grim determination to stand against the horrors of the night, the humans of Gavony are the most well-rounded people of Innistrad.	ASPECT:BENEFIT|Ability Score Increase: Your ability scores each increase by 1.	ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Gavony ~ Ability Score Increase
Kessig	KEY:Provincial Origin ~ Kessig	TYPE:Innistrad Human ~ Provincial Origin.SpecialQuality	CATEGORY:Special Ability	DESC:For the Kessiger, life is work. Kessigers are farmers, millers, weavers, and stonemasons, living close to the land and working hard for every meal. This makes them self-reliant, pragmatic, and plainspoken.	ASPECT:BENEFIT|Ability Score Increase: Your Dexterity and Wisdom scores each increase by 1. Forest Folk: You have proficiency in the Survival skill. Fleet of Foot: Your base walking speed is 40 feet. Sure-Footed: When you use the Dash action, difficult terrain doesn’t cost you extra movement on that turn. Spring Attack: When you make a melee attack against a creature, you don’t provoke opportunity attacks from that creature for the rest of your turn, whether you hit or not.	ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Kessig ~ Ability Score Increase		ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Kessig ~ Forest Folk			ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Kessig ~ Fleet of Foot			ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Kessig ~ Sure-Footed		ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Kessig ~ Spring Attack		
Nephalia	KEY:Provincial Origin ~ Nephalia	TYPE:Innistrad Human ~ Provincial Origin.SpecialQuality	CATEGORY:Special Ability	DESC:Beneath an ever-present shroud of fog billowing in from the sea, the people of Nephalia maintain a semblance of normalcy, buying and selling goods from across Innistrad in their bustling markets, setting out to sea in tiny fishing boats, or tilling the soggy earth in waterlogged fields.	ASPECT:BENEFIT|Ability Score Increase: Your Intelligence and Charisma scores each increase by 1. Breadth of Knowledge:You gain proficiency in any combination of four skills or with four tools of your choice.	ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Nephalia ~ Ability Score Increase		ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Nephalia ~ Breadth of Knowledge		
Stensia	KEY:Provincial Origin ~ Stensia	TYPE:Innistrad Human ~ Provincial Origin.SpecialQuality	CATEGORY:Special Ability	DESC:Countless generations of hardship and proximity to the vampire strongholds—leading to lost children and neighbors—have taught Stensians to guard their hearts. They are proud and fervent in their beliefs but seem brusque or even cold to the people of other provinces.	ASPECT:BENEFIT|Ability Score Increase. Your Strength and Constitution scores each increase by 1. Daunting: You have proficiency in the Intimidation skill. Tough: Your hit point maximum increases by 2, and it increases by 2 every time you gain a level.	ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Stensia ~ Ability Score Increase	ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Stensia ~ Daunting				ABILITY:Human Trait|AUTOMATIC|Stensia ~ Tough			

